        "Wrote <strong>custom HLSL shaders</strong> for real-time chroma keying, compositing live camera feeds with pre-recorded celebrity footage",
        'Integrated <strong>hardware systems</strong>: 55" IR touch frames, DSLR cameras, card swipe units, cash payment tracking',
        "Designed <strong>offline-first architecture</strong> with local caching for multi-gigabyte video assets; maintenance mode for updates",
        "Built backend with <strong>Strapi + AWS</strong> for geo-targeted content delivery across mall/theatre locations",
      ],
      stack: "Unity, C#, Strapi, AWS, Stripe",
    },
    {
      role: "Freelance & Game Developer",
      company: "Self-Employed",
      period: "2017 – 2020",
      meta: "Mobile Games · Client Projects",
      desc: "Solo indie developer who shipped published games to iOS and Android. Learned systems thinking, performance optimization, and end-to-end product ownership.",
      points: [
        "Published <strong>Pocket Hopper</strong> and <strong>Exile</strong> to Google Play Store",
        "Mastered multi-disciplinary skills out of necessity: Unity, C#, Blender (3D), Photoshop, Illustrator",
        "Built foundation for thinking in terms of <strong>state, responsiveness, and frame-budget constraints</strong>—habits that transfer directly to frontend performance",
      ],
      stack: "Unity, C#, Blender, Photoshop, Illustrator",
    },
  ],
  skills: [
    {
      label: "Frontend",
      value:
        "Next.js, React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion, Zustand, CSS-in-JS",
    },
    {
      label: "Web3",
      value: "Wagmi, Viem, Ethers.js, WalletConnect",
    },
    { label: "Mobile", value: "Flutter, GetX, Unity (C#)" },
    {
      label: "Design",
      value: "Figma, Photoshop, Illustrator, Blender",
    },
    {
      label: "Backend",
      value: "Node.js, Elysia.js, PostgreSQL, GCP, Firebase, Supabase",
    },
    {
      label: "Other",
      value:
        "Git, CI/CD, Vercel, Performance optimization, Offline-first architecture",
    },
  ],
  projects: [
    {
      name: "matchaGo",
      desc: "Restaurant management platform with custom dashboard and customer app. Backended by Elysia.js, migrated from Supabase to Drizzle (PostgreSQL) + BetterAuth. Features WebSockets for real-time updates; hosted on Cloudflare + GCP.",
    },
    {
      name: "Nuggets",
      desc: "Flutter news app with offline-first architecture (ObjectBox), BlurHash image placeholders, and FCM push notifications.",
    },
  ],
};
---

<Layout title="Bharadwaj Palakurthy | Resume A4">
  <div class="resume-a4-wrapper">
    <div class="resume-a4">
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="profile-section">
          <h1 class="name">
            {content.name.split(" ")[0]}<br />{content.name.split(" ")[1]}
          </h1>
          <p class="role">{content.role}</p>

          <div class="contact">
            {
              content.contact.map((c) => (
                <a href={c.link} class="contact-link">
                  {c.text}
                </a>
              ))
            }
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h2>Skills</h2>
          <div class="skills-list">
            {
              content.skills.map((skill) => (
                <div class="skill-item">
                  <strong>{skill.label}</strong>
                  <p>{skill.value}</p>
                </div>
              ))
            }
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h2>Projects</h2>
          <div class="projects-list">
            {
              content.projects.map((p) => (
                <div class="project-item">
                  <h3>{p.name}</h3>
                  <p>{p.desc}</p>
                </div>
              ))
            }
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <main class="main-content">
        <section class="summary">
          <h2>Summary</h2>
          <p>{content.summary}</p>
        </section>

        <section class="experience">
          <h2>Experience</h2>
          {
            content.experience.map((job) => (
              <div class="job-card">
                <div class="job-header">
                  <h3>{job.role}</h3>
                  <span class="company">{job.company}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="job-subheader">
                  <span class="date">{job.period}</span>
                  <span class="meta">{job.meta}</span>
                </div>

                <p class="desc">{job.desc}</p>
                <ul>
                  {job.points.map((point) => (
                    <li set:html={point} />
                  ))}
                </ul>
                <div class="stack-wrap">
                  <p class="stack">
                    <span>Stack:</span> {job.stack}
                  </p>
                </div>

                {/* {job.extra && <p class="impact" set:html={job.extra} />} */}
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>

    <style>
      /* A4 Wrapper for previewing on screen */
      .resume-a4-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        background: #525659;
        padding: 2rem 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .resume-a4 {
        width: 210mm;
        min-height: 297mm; /* A4 Height */
        background: #fff;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 75mm 1fr; /* Fixed sidebar width */
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        font-family:
          "Inter",
          system-ui,
          -apple-system,
          sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        overflow: hidden; /* Ensure no bleed */
      }

      /* Global Reset inside Resume */
      .resume-a4 * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      .sidebar {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 10mm 6mm;
        border-right: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      }

      .main-content {
        padding: 10mm 10mm;
      }

      /* Sidebar Styles */
      .name {
        font-size: 20pt;
        line-height: 1.1;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin-bottom: 5mm;
        color: #111;
      }

      .role {
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #222;
        margin-bottom: 8mm;
        line-height: 1.4;
        font-size: 10pt;
      }

      .contact {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2mm;
        font-size: 8.5pt;
        margin-bottom: 12mm;
      }

      .contact-link {
        color: #111;
        text-decoration: none;
        word-break: break-all;
      }

      .sidebar-block {
        margin-bottom: 12mm;
      }

      .sidebar-block h2 {
        font-size: 9pt;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        color: #222;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #999;
        padding-bottom: 2mm;
        margin-bottom: 4mm;
      }

      .traits-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .traits-list li {
        margin-bottom: 4mm;
      }

      .traits-list strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 1mm;
        color: #111;
        font-size: 9pt;
      }

      .traits-list p {
        font-size: 8.5pt;
        color: #222;
        line-height: 1.4;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .skill-item {
        margin-bottom: 2mm;
        font-size: 7.5pt;
      }

      .skill-item strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.5mm;
        color: #000;
        font-size: 8pt;
      }

      .skill-item p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #222;
        line-height: 1.2;
        font-size: 10pt;
      }

      /* Main Content Styles */
      section {
        margin-bottom: 8mm;
      }

      section h2 {
        font-size: 16pt;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin-bottom: 5mm;
        color: #111;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #111;
        padding-bottom: 1mm;
        display: inline-block;
      }

      .summary p {
        font-size: 10pt;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #111;
      }

      .job-card {
        margin-bottom: 7mm;
        break-inside: avoid; /* Prevent breaking across pages if content overflows */
      }

      .job-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: baseline;
        margin-bottom: 1mm;
      }

      .job-header h3 {
        font-size: 12pt;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0;
        color: #111;
      }

      .job-header .company {
        font-size: 10pt;
        color: #222;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .job-subheader {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        font-size: 9pt;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 2mm;
      }

      .date {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #000;
      }

      .meta {
        font-style: italic;
      }

      .desc {
        margin-bottom: 2mm;
        line-height: 1.4;
        font-size: 9.5pt;
        color: #111;
      }

      .experience ul {
        margin: 2mm 0 3mm 5mm;
        color: #111;
        font-size: 9.5pt;
      }

      .experience li {
        margin-bottom: 1mm;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      .stack-wrap {
        margin-bottom: 2mm;
      }

      .stack {
        font-family: "SF Mono", "Monaco", monospace;
        font-size: 8pt;
        background: #f3f4f6;
        padding: 1mm 2mm;
        border-radius: 2px;
        display: inline-block;
        color: #111;
      }

      .stack span {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #000;
      }

      .impact {
        margin-top: 2mm;
        font-size: 9pt;
        font-style: italic;
        color: #222;
        background: #fffdf0;
        padding: 2mm;
        border-left: 2px solid #f1c40f;
      }

      .project-item h3 {
        font-size: 11pt;
        margin: 0 0 1mm 0;
        color: #000;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .project-item p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #222;
        font-size: 9.5pt;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      /* Print Media Query */
      @media print {
        body {
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          background: #fff;
        }
        .resume-a4-wrapper {
          padding: 0;
          background: #fff;
          display: block;
        }
        .resume-a4 {
          width: 100%;
          min-height: auto;
          box-shadow: none;
          margin: 0;
          border: none;
        }
        @page {
          size: A4;
          margin: 0;
        }
        a {
          text-decoration: none;
          color: inherit;
        }
      }

      .projects-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 3mm;
      }

      .projects-list .project-item h3 {
        font-size: 9pt;
        margin: 0 0 0.5mm 0;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .projects-list .project-item p {
        font-size: 8pt;
        line-height: 1.3;
        color: #333;
      }
    </style>
  </div></Layout
>
